title: [Maelstrom Bay, Underwater]
description: Light green water above, deep green water below, green water all around.  Club-fingered coral grows on a reef wall to the west.  A wide patch of sargassum on the surface hinders the sunlight.  The long, flat-bladed streamers hanging beneath the sargassum sway and undulate sinuously in a green dance.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, up, down
